inferModel_select.label: Model Selection
inferModel_select.title: Choose the pre-trained model to use for generating images.

startInfer.label: Generate
startInfer.title: Begin generating images based on the selected model and settings.

stopInfer.label: Cancel
stopInfer.title: Stop the current image generation process.

aspectButtons.label: Aspect Ratio
aspectButtons.title: Select the desired aspect ratio for the generated images.

infer_prompt.label: Prompt
infer_prompt.title: Enter a prompt to guide the image generation process.

infer_negative_prompt.label: Negative Prompt
infer_negative_prompt.title: Enter a negative prompt to guide the image generation process.

infer_txt2img.label: Txt2Img
infer_txt2img.title: Generate images from text prompts using a pre-trained model.

infer_inpaint.label: Inpaint
infer_inpaint.title: Fill in missing or corrupted parts of an image using a pre-trained model.

infer_img2img.label: Img2Img
infer_img2img.title: Translate images from one domain to another using a pre-trained model.

inpaintEditor.label: Input Image:
inpaintEditor.title: Upload an image to use as input for the inpainting model.

infer_seed.label: Seed
infer_seed.title: Enter a random seed value to use for the image generation process.

infer_sag.label: Self-Attention-Guidance
infer_sag.title: Use self-attention guidance during the image generation process.

enableControlNet.label: Enable ControlNet
enableControlNet.title: Enable the use of a control network during the image generation process.

controlnetType.label: Controlnet Type:
controlnetType.title: Select the type of control network to use for the image generation process.

controlnetPreProcess.label: Preprocess
controlnetPreProcess.title: Enable preprocessing of the input images before using them with the control network.

controlnetBatchInput.label: Batch Input
controlnetBatchInput.title: Upload a batch of images to use as input for the control network.

controlnetEditor.label: Input Image:
controlnetEditor.title: Upload an image to use as input for the control network.

autoLoadResolutionOn.label: Auto-load resolution:
autoLoadResolutionOn.title: Automatically load the input image's resolution to use as output resolution for the control network.

controlnetBatchUsePrompt.label: Use prompt from input images:
controlnetBatchUsePrompt.title: Use the prompts specified in the input images for the image generation process.

controlnetBatchFind.label: Find:
controlnetBatchFind.title: Enter the text to search for in the control network's input images.

controlnetBatchReplace.label: Replace:
controlnetBatchReplace.title: Enter the replacement text for the control network's input images.
